## Hints for Future Agents

- This branch is the bottom of a stack. The parent
  `andrew/adk-otel-integration` (ADK ↔ Weave OTel integration) emits
  `gen_ai.usage.reasoning.output_tokens` as the canonical wire name and
  *does not need* `additional_aliases` to function. The aliases preserve
  (a) old stored data using `gen_ai.usage.reasoning_tokens` and (b)
  ADK-native (un-Weave-patched) spans that emit
  `gen_ai.usage.experimental.reasoning_tokens`. So this PR is a soft
  dependency for ADK — useful but not gating.
- The mechanism is generic; future naming drift cases register more
  `additional_aliases` without further plumbing.
- Local `master` was stale (40cb57e). Always branch off `origin/master`
  when carving a child PR out of a long-lived feature branch in this
  repo — local master can lag origin by days.

